overview.en: BFC is the world's first automatic quantitative trading platform for value-preserving and arbitrage digital assets created by a top quantitative trading team. It aims to use advanced artificial intelligence technology to automate transactions so that everyone can easily earn digital assets.
overview.zh: BFC是由顶尖的量化交易团队打造的全球首款保值套利型数字资产自动量化交易平台，旨在利用先进的人工智能技术，实现交易的自动化，让每一个人都能轻松赚取数字资产。
